oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmie Rehearsing Session - Four Songs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording is of Jimmie Snow rehearsing four songs with two unidentified guitar tunes. This recording is from April 7, 1955.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Jimmie Snow;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) Go Back You Fool [fades in and out] (Jimmie Snow) -- (02:06) Flame of Love (Jimmie Snow) -- (03:17) Someone Else's Heartache (Jimmie Snow) -- (04:52) Beginning of I Care No More (Jimmie Snow) -- (05:01) Snow clears throat and starts I Care No More again -- (06:25) Unidentified tune (Jimmie Snow) -- (08:29) Unidentified guitar tune (Jimmie Snow)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Snow, Jimmie Rodgers;
